      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's so creepy. i even noticed that if i stay in the kitchen for a while the signal drops, but as soon as i walk back to the bedroom it spikes again. do you think they have some kind of sensor in their router that triggers when they detect a specific device moving? like a motion sensor but for WiFi signals?",
